				\begin{document}$$10\text {km}^2$$\end{document}10km2 in Colorado (Miller et al. 2006); given WTD home ranges are roughly \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
